title: 297. Andy & DJ CTI: Missouri Bill On Ivermectin Effectiveness, Biden Blaming Republicans & BLM Co-Founder Tax Filings
itunes:title: 297. Andy & DJ CTI: Missouri Bill On Ivermectin Effectiveness, Biden Blaming Republicans & BLM Co-Founder Tax Filings
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Missouri's passing of a bill that prohibits pharmacists from questioning doctors who prescribe Ivermectin to treat Covid-19, President Biden's lackluster livestream attendance in which he blames Republicans for a Buffalo store shooting, and tax filings that reveal mischievous spending of donation money from the co-founder of BLM.
